    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience automotive excellence with this impeccably preserved specimen. Presented in true showroom condition, this vehicle has been curated for the discerning driver who demands nothing less than perfection. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior, reflects a history of meticulous care and climate-controlled storage. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a benchmark example that performs as impressively as it looks.",
