      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a masterpiece of automotive history that feels as though it was plucked straight from a collector\u2019s dream. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a portal to an era of uncompromising elegance. The bodywork catches the sunlight with a mirror-like depth, while the interior welcomes you with the rich, unmistakable aroma of perfectly preserved upholstery. Every curve tells a story of pristine care and quiet Sunday drives through the countryside. To turn the key is to hear a mechanical symphony, a smooth, confident purr that promises endless horizons. This is a rare opportunity to own a legend that has been cherished like a family heirloom, waiting for its next chapter with you behind the wheel.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
