    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by to look at my absolute pride and joy. I've pampered this beauty since day one\u2014honestly, it\u2019s been garage-kept, hand-washed every weekend, and still has that wonderful 'new car' feel when you slide into the driver's seat. It runs like an absolute dream, smooth as silk and ready for a new home. I noticed one tiny, tiny little mark on the rim from a stray pebble, but you'd honestly have to squint to see it! This is a rare find in such stunning shape, and I\u2019d love to see it go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Why don't you come over, have a coffee, and see it for yourself?",
      "price": 46500.0,
