    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered here is a meticulously curated example of driver-centric engineering. This chassis has been treated to comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a full VANOS bulletproofing and rear subframe reinforcement to mitigate factory torsional stress points. The S54 power plant exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders, delivering a crisp, high-revving induction note through an upgraded carbon intake. We\u2019ve optimized the suspension kinematics with corner-balanced coilovers, ensuring the roll center remains stable under heavy lateral loads. Every bushing has been replaced with high-durometer poly to sharpen turn-in response without compromising NVH. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, reflecting a lifetime of climate-controlled storage. This is a turn-key performance machine for the discerning purist who values mechanical integrity and drivetrain rigidity.",
      "price": 48900.0,
